# level-five-book consumer ontology — this project needs zero project-specific
# facts: level-five-book-pack is fully self-contained, driven entirely from its
# own pack ontology.ttl individuals (366 book:Chapter + 366 book:Listing).
# Prefix declarations only, matching the pack's book: namespace
# (see ../../packs/level-five-book-pack/ontology.ttl).

@prefix book: <http://seanchatmangpt.github.io/packs/level-five-book#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
